sentence: through which states does the longest river in texas run ?
sentence-with-vars: through which states does the longest river in state0 run ?
sql: select river.traverse from river where river.length = ( select max ( river.length ) from river where river.traverse = ' texas ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select river.traverse from river where river.length = ( select max ( river.length ) from river where river.traverse = ' state0 ' ) ;
